<item>
            <title>[LU-474] fix release build issues</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-474</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need to fix release builds so that kernels don&apos;t have git hashes in their version.  This is done because a kernel is reused from a previous not-on-tag build.  I guess release builds should force a kernel build.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Need to allow the -wc1 and -WC1 monikers in tags.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="11259">LU-474</key>
            <summary>fix release build issues</summary>
