                            <comment id="45858" author="brian" created="Tue, 2 Oct 2012 09:30:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;OK.  So given the review pointers you provided I see only an update to the lustre/doc/VERSIONING file and nothing else.  Updating this file does nothing at all to solve the problem this bug is open for.  The problem this bug describes requires a build code fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
